00:43:28,956 --> 00:43:30,218
that cannot be broken.

806
00:43:30,257 --> 00:43:32,054
l never believed that
until l went...

807
00:43:32,093 --> 00:43:33,117
Julian...

808
00:43:33,160 --> 00:43:34,525
Hmm?

809
00:43:36,864 --> 00:43:38,195
Oh.

810
00:43:38,232 --> 00:43:40,700
